    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Alma lavacrorum de sa<supplied reason="lost">xis deci</supplied>do lympha <lb n="2"/>et sunt ex lapide perfecta<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">e balnea</supplied>e pulchrae <lb n="3"/>laetis inque locis natus la<supplied reason="lost">cus id</supplied> tamen ipsis <lb n="4"/>tunc cum sospes erat coniux s<supplied reason="lost">acravit</supplied> in usum <lb n="5"/>emeritis quondam Alexand<supplied reason="lost">reo</supplied> nomine dignae <lb n="6"/>raucisoni lapidoso cadunt <supplied reason="lost">de fo</supplied>nte liquores <lb n="7"/>tam laudati operis dominus <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">famosus</supplied> et auctor <lb n="8"/>in suae memoriam voluit con<supplied reason="lost">secrare</supplied> maritae <lb n="9"/>ut tamen et lector nomen <supplied reason="lost">cognosce</supplied>re possis <lb n="10"/>singulae declarant exordia l<supplied reason="lost">itter</supplied>ae primae <lb n="11"/>Aelia cum Tertia subole de coniuge <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Faus</supplied>ta
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Maße des Inschriftfeldes (nach Abklatsch): 40 x 61 cm. Lesung und Ergänzungsvorschläge nach Marković, ZPE 56, 1984. (B): Kleinere Abweichungen in Lesung und Ergänzung. Der Name Ael. Tertius ist aus den Anfangsbuchstaben der Zeilen 1-9 gebildet.</p>
            </div>
